      "text": "はい！　サニピが出演するお正月のテレビ番組に\n芸人のホットドッグさんも出るって聞いて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I heard that on the New Year's TV show where\nSunny Peace will appear‚ the comedian Mr.Hot Dog will also be on…",
