      "text": "ああ、そのことか\n企画コーナーでさくらと羽根つき対決するんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ I see. Is that about the planned section\nwhere Sakura will have a Hanetsuki （Japanese badminton） showdown?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
